= Prayer =
'''Sphere:''' Special  
'''Level:''' 5  
'''Range:''' 60 yds  
'''Components:''' V, S, M (cross or holy water)  
'''Duration:''' 1 turn  
'''Casting Time:''' 5 rounds  
'''Area of Effect:''' 30-ft radius  
'''Saving Throw:''' None  

== Description ==
Allies gain +1 bonus to attack, damage, and saving throws. Enemies take -1 penalties. Effects only apply while the priest prays.

== Special Notes ==
* Treated as a [[Prayer]] in this campaign.
* All casting times and durations are increased by an order of magnitude (round → turn, turn → hour, etc).
* Requires cross and/or holy water.
